3x lamb shank
3x lamb neck
15L of water, boiled, till 4L of liquid
Constant descumming
Demeat, strain stock
Strain the stock, fridge, cold, remove fat 

Heat up strained stock
Add:
Two bunch spring onon
Big bunch of dill
Two head of cos lettuce
All chopped finely

Half cup white medium rice
Cook till rice is cooked, approx 25 mins

Three eggs, beat till foam
Lemon to taste (around 3/4 of a coffee mug)
Combine egg and lemon juice
While whisking, slowly add hot soup, double the volume

Let soup cool for 10-15 mins, and then add egg mixture in...
Black pepper to taste
